name: Spaceballs
body:
## Spaceballs!

It's like Dodgeball in Space!
It's like you are a tiny red Ghandi dodging large blue shadowed temptations of religious intolerance!
What...?

Never mind. Move with WASD.
Hold and release for more power or push multiple times to speed up/change velocity!
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
